<h3>Motor System:</h3>
<p><em>Inspect for Bulk (mentioned under general inspection) and Tone
        (mentioned under palpation).</em></p>
<p><em>Power (MRC Scale: 0-5, though not explicitly graded in video,
        resistance is applied).</em></p>
